            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ulpiae <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Aristoni<lb break="no" n="3"/>c<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> coniu<lb break="no" n="4"/>gi <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Valeri <lb n="5"/>Maximiani <lb n="6"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>stratores
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: nicht vor der Zeit zwischen 183 und 185 n. Chr., als M. Valerius Maximianus während seiner kaiserlichen Legatur in Numidien Konsul geworden war.</p>
            </div>
